ygData.messageBody:

(and loads of cash), finally made it to 140 skill.

need... sigh).

couple question though, for those who are making and
selling rebreathers. 1)it is a "medium plate helm" that
is needed for rebreather, right? (i have the book but just
want to make sure) 2)how much are you guys selling rebreather
for?

thx for all the helps in advance.

Maruk
Tinker Master 140 of Bertoxxulous
50 Nerfomancer Gnome
